{"tid":2018304,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Marvel電影角色實力Top 5，  你會點樣排名？","createTime":"2020-05-15T14:00:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-16T13:13:00.000Z","uid":353419,"like":3,"dislike":109,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"23ffbc5bd2b7068054ddf1d17b38cd64e09a2b30","tid":2018304,"uid":353419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T14:00:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">5.蜘蛛俠：</span><br />\n<br />\n佢擁有蜘蛛感應，佢的感知能力非常強，佢可以勉強避得開快銀的高速攻擊，就算驚奇隊長幾高攻都冇用，因為打唔中蜘蛛俠。其實第二集講緊佢的感知能力進步緊，理論上，去到顛峰可以100%Miss。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uBN3Mx0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuBN3Mx0.jpg&h=2b8bba43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4.古一<br />\n<br />\n雖然驚奇隊長同紅巫的體術魔術好強，但係古一的幻術更強，佢可以一野拍走佢地個靈魂，同埋用時空間術轉移攻擊，甚至分屍，可惜不及美國隊長的主角光環。Thanos一直唔敢侵略地球，因為古一未死。可惜QuickSilver太快，古一反應唔切。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y39JMya.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY39JMya.jpg&h=f03215a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3.QuickSilver：<br />\n<br />\n天下無功唯快不破，佢被天啟捉得住唔合符邏輯，正常佢啲動作慢到定格，不過快銀實力未到頂，因為佢攻擊力太低，需要開發新術，或者比把雷神斧頭佢，一下瞬身術砍落Thanos心口，大結局了。同埋繼續進步可以達到光速，當Thanos殺哂隊友果陣，佢可以穿越時空，阻止佢出手，殺埋佢。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2tvwVrQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2tvwVrQ.jpg&h=8af6afb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2..Ironman：<br />\n<br />\n，實力唔一定係正面對決，任何角色都有弱點，Ironman可以搵出Thanos的弱點，然後擬定作戰方案，最後整左特制新手套，陰左Thanos一獲。再加上佢實力無上限，繼續整新科技，會一直變強。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HtpmydQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHtpmydQ.jpg&h=70469c64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1.美國隊長 <br />\n<br />\n雖然佢只係強化人類，但你見佢同洛基打五五波，同Thanos打都係五五波，一集比一集勁，你就知唔可以用硬件衡量佢實力，事實上佢人氣太高，所以有主角光環，根據呢個設定，佢係電影入面係無敵，就算將來出現比Thanos更強敵人，佢都照樣五五波。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Oj7Lfsk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOj7Lfsk.jpg&h=528a28ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>補充：</strong></span><br />\n<br />\nThanos五甲不入，佢冇手套根本大把角色勁過佢，而手套需要公用物品，就好似公廁或者巴士咁。任何角色帶左手套都變最強，咁冇野值得討論，所以唔計。"},{"pid":"264fa9d7a5871fd1026a1cc71ee5932802a5c8a6","tid":2018304,"uid":96941,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T14:08:14.000Z","msg":"電影唔用手套都隻揪打嬴HULK喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e341e4b4175352936e0f5173d9a03f53263cbb56","tid":2018304,"uid":157261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T05:36:02.000Z","msg":"13負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55d07787b715aef2f588363eff054c5ca8f18b24","tid":2018304,"uid":23085,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T05:43:27.000Z","msg":"電影來講我諗係<br />\nCM<br />\nHulk<br />\nDoctor Strange<br />\nScarlet Witch<br />\nQuick Sliver"},{"pid":"44fc2b055b2a4e2a6f801594a6cc5c8032991b10","tid":2018304,"uid":121984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T05:47:41.000Z","msg":"實際上既實力一定唔係咁排 不過你計埋主角光環"},{"pid":"2229e3b27229d21d319969f302c1c958661de191","tid":2018304,"uid":64953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T05:50:20.000Z","msg":"六石Thanos<br />\nDormammu<br />\nCap Marvel<br />\nThor<br />\nDr Strange"},{"pid":"3e394e510ee32cf01a120598dab6978381f02cc3","tid":2018304,"uid":213496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T05:53:23.000Z","msg":"Thanos<br />\nCaptain marvel<br />\nThor<br />\nDoctor strange<br />\nScarlet witch"},{"pid":"29670935f38791cb8a245301e2d4ad21cc9fd142","tid":2018304,"uid":37234,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T05:55:54.000Z","msg":"幾錢一個月?"},{"pid":"81e3edb7e304bb6474a40bb70c1a227f89a304a7","tid":2018304,"uid":277432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-0